## <a id="2-3-0"></a> v2.3.0

**Release Date: MMMM DD, 2019**

### Features

New features and changes in this release:

* On-Demand Plans are now configurable dynamically, see [Configure On-Demand Plan Settings](./installing.html#on-demand-plan-config).

* Service instance and broker metrics are emitted in Prometheus format. For
general information about metrics,
see [Monitoring <%= vars.product_name %>](./monitoring.html).

* Errands now have impact warnings when service instance downtime is expected.

* Syslog configuration is now delegated to <%= vars.ops_manager %>


